Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.15,pm2,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.13\an4\pos(780,177)\frz339\3c&HFFFFFF&}正因為有您陪著
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.15,pm2,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.13\an4\pos(741,237)\frz339\3c&HFFFFFF&}我才能跟玉來同學開口
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.15,pm2,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.13\an4\pos(699,297)\frz339\3c&HFFFFFF&}真的很感謝您
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.65,pm2,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.13\frz339\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1206,516)}玉來同學說她相信狩生同學 會等她 我也一樣
